                                        1643,
                                        1190,
                                        1989
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "To investigate the effectiveness of the proposed methods, we conducted extensive experiments on three large- scale datasets [9, 38, 64] as well as off- the- shelf cameras. This evaluation demonstrated that our method notably outperforms conventional geometry- based [32, 41] and learningbased [33, 52, 53] methods. The major contributions of our study are summarized as follows:"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
